<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٨٤٩ - وعن <span class="c2">(عبيد)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> اللَّه بن أبي <span class="c2">(يزيد)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(عن ابن الزبير)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>: ﴿لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَنْ تَبْتَغُوا فَضْلًا مِنْ رَبِّكُمْ﴾ <span class="c2">(قالا)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>: <span class="c2">(في مواسم الحج)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
